Package: nomine
Type: Package
Title: Classify Names by Gender, U.S. Ethnicity, and Leaf Nationality
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: c(person("Charles", "Crabtree", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                     email = "crabtreedcharles@gmail.com"),
              person("Volha", "Chykina", role = c("aut")),
              person("Micah", "Gell-Redman", role = c("aut")),
              person("Christian", "Chacua", role = c("aut"), email = "christian-mauricio.chacua-delgado@u-bordeaux.fr"))
Description: Functions to use the 'NamePrism' API <https://name-prism.com/api> or 'NamSor' API v2 <https://v2.namsor.com> for classifying names based on gender, 6 U.S. ethnicities, or 39 leaf nationalities. Updated to work with current API endpoints.
